{"title":"过村寨","authors":["潘行受"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":9,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"过村寨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公安战士　潘行受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马蹄声由远而近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村寨过来一队巡逻兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么你们每到这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总要勒住手上的缰绳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是要摸一摸路边的杨柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们亲手栽的，已成绿荫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是要掬一掬河里的清水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们亲手挖的，洗洗风尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几声畅笑道出了战士的满怀豪情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士初到边疆时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把春天引到了村寨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天重过这里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友呵，你听，你听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛丛火红的格桑花下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘来了笛声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年黄沙塞住的羌笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹出了生活的赞美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而挽住寨外春天的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是边防战士和寨上人民。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}